headline: Californian billionaires flee potential one-off 5% wealth tax
description: In 2024, California had 255 billionaires, more than any other state. A state ballot initiative aimed at taxing the state's wealthiest residents could be put to a public vote in autumn 2026.

headline: 2026 Golden Globes: 'One Battle After Another' sweeps Best Film, Best Director and Best Screenplay
description: Paul Thomas Anderson's screwball thriller entered the night with nine nominations. Anderson won Best Director, while Teyanna Taylor snagged Best Supporting Female. The film's only major upset was its star Leonardo DiCaprio losing best actor to Timothée Chalamet for 'Marty Supreme.'
